 <!-- Introduction -->
 <!-- The introduction should start as shown: -->
 <purpose>
   <p>
     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the
     representation of the activities involved in the specification, performance and monitoring of work, and for the documents that define these activities.
   </p>
 </purpose>

 <!-- Items in scope -->
 <inscope>
   <li>activities that specify, perform and monitor work with an AEC project;</li>
   <li>approval, disapproval or abandonment of activities;</li>
   <li>documents that specify activities or that control activities</li>
 </inscope>

 <!-- Items out of scope -->
 <outscope>
   <li>dates at which an activity begins and ends;</li>
   <li>the performers of an activity;</li>
   <li>the material involved in an activity;</li>
   <li>the contract under which an activity is performed.</li>
 </outscope>


